**  MSG (ERROR MESSAGE )
E-01 DATA INSTRUCTION <1 2 3>
E-02 INPUT PLATING MAKER
E-03 PLATING MAKER ISN'T RIGHT
E-04 INPUT PERIOD START DAY
E-05 PERIOD START DAY ISN'T RIGHT
E-06 INPUT PERIOD EXIT DAY
E-07 PERIOD EXIT DAY ISN'T RIGHT
E-08 PERIOD START DAY IS BIGGER THAN PERIOD EXIT DAY
E-09 THERE ISN'T APPLICABLE DATA
